- Install the ADB Commanads for VSCode extension.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------


- Now you have to add the path correctly to the 
        platform-tools

in my case it’s

“C:\Users\Hardy1\AppData\Local\Android\Sdk\platform-tools “
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------


- Enable usb debugging in your device .
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- In the VScode hit Ctrl+shift+p and select ADB::Connect to device IP

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- you can connect your phone without any extension simply by followings these steps :

   1.plug your phone via usb.

  2.open your vs terminal ( you can open the terminal using Ctrl+ `)

  adb tcpip 5555
  adb connect [YOUR_IP_address]
